---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Pre-Enforcement Compliance Preparation - AILEX Consulting" description="Strategic implementation framework preparing organisations for EU AI Act enforcement. Comprehensive governance development and documentation standards.">
  <Header />
  
  <main>
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-parchment to-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
            Pre-Enforcement Compliance Preparation
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-advisory-grey max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Strategic implementation framework preparing organisations for August 2025 enforcement 
            combined with governance system development and documentation standards.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-200 p-8 mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Service Framework</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="border-l-4 border-innovation-indigo bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-r-lg">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Module 1: Governance Framework Development</h3>
              <p class="text-advisory-grey mb-4">
                Comprehensive AI governance structure establishment addressing regulatory requirements 
                and organisational needs.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-advisory-grey">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-innovation-indigo mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  AI governance committee formation with defined responsibilities
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-innovation-indigo mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  Policy framework development addressing Article 4 literacy requirements
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-innovation-indigo mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  Risk management system design incorporating bias detection protocols
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="border-l-4 border-compliance-green bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-r-lg">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Module 2: Documentation Standardisation</h3>
              <p class="text-advisory-grey mb-4">
                Comprehensive documentation framework ensuring audit readiness and regulatory compliance.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-advisory-grey">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-compliance-green mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  Technical documentation templates for high-risk systems
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-compliance-green mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  Record-keeping systems ensuring audit trail compliance
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-compliance-green mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  Transparency mechanisms for user interaction with AI systems
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="border-l-4 border-caution-amber bg-amber-50 p-6 rounded-r-lg">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Module 3: Process Integration</h3>
              <p class="text-advisory-grey mb-4">
                Systematic integration of compliance processes with existing organisational workflows.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-advisory-grey">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-caution-amber mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  Quality management system implementation
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-caution-amber mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  Human oversight protocols for high-risk applications
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-caution-amber mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  Post-market monitoring frameworks with incident reporting
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-200 p-8 mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Investment & Timeline</h2>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">Implementation Timeline</h3>
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <div class="font-semibold text-european-blue">Weeks 1-2</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-slate-600">Foundation establishment</div>
                </div>
                <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <div class="font-semibold text-european-blue">Weeks 3-4</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-slate-600">Documentation standardisation</div>
                </div>
                <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <div class="font-semibold text-european-blue">Weeks 5-6</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-slate-600">Process integration</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">Investment Framework</h3>
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <div class="text-lg font-semibold text-european-blue">£18,000 - £35,000</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-slate-600">Complete implementation programme</div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-sm text-advisory-grey mt-4">
                  <strong>Payment Structure:</strong>
                  <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1">
                    <li>• 40% upon contract signing</li>
                    <li>• 35% at milestone completion</li>
                    <li>• 25% upon final delivery</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 border border-transparent text-lg font-medium rounded-lg text-white bg-innovation-indigo hover:bg-european-blue transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1">
            Begin Preparation
            <svg class="ml-2 -mr-1 w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>